         <abstract id="aspace_81bda2d7fb2209ad0c950b5cc28fb58d">The records consist of correspondence, lists, circulars, flyers, photographs, news releases, scrapbooks, an audiotape, and memoranda documenting the operations and activities of the Yale University Federation of University Employees Local No. 35, AFL-CIO at Yale University.</abstract>
